# Customer Inquiry & Claim Notification

1. Thank you for reaching out to us. We have received your inquiry and are committed to providing you with the information you need.

2. If your request is related to a claim, we would like to inform you that your claim is currently under investigation. We will notify you promptly once the investigation is complete and share any planned adjustments or outcomes related to your claim.

3. If you have any further questions or require additional assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us. We value your satisfaction and are here to support you throughout this process.

4. Thank you for choosing our services.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
